						<p class="sport-intro">Hockey equipment is among the most challenging to store. Skates, pads, sticks, and gear all require specialized storage solutions. Our hockey lockers are built to handle it all.</p>
						<h3>Built for Hockey Equipment</h3>
						<ul class="feature-list">
							<li>Reinforced construction for heavy gear</li>
							<li>Specific compartments for skates</li>
							<li>Stick storage solutions</li>
							<li>Ventilated compartments for pads</li>
							<li>Helmet and glove storage</li>
							<li>Equipment drying features</li>
						</ul>
						<h3>Why Wood for Hockey?</h3>
						<p>Wood's natural properties help manage moisture from wet equipment. The durable construction withstands the weight of hockey gear, while the professional appearance matches the elite nature of hockey programs.</p>
						<a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Get Hockey Locker Quote</a>
					</div>
					<div class="sport-detail-image">
						<div class="image-placeholder">
							<span>Hockey Locker Installation</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Basketball -->
			<div id="basketball" class="sport-detail">
				<div class="sport-detail-grid">
					<div class="sport-detail-content">
						<div class="sport-image-large">
							<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1519869325934-2813331509ce?w=1200&q=80" alt="Basketball" />
						</div>
						<h2>Basketball Lockers</h2>
						<p class="sport-intro">Basketball lockers need to be sleek, organized, and professional. Our basketball lockers provide perfect storage for shoes, uniforms, and personal items while maintaining a clean, modern appearance.</p>
						<h3>Optimized for Basketball</h3>
						<ul class="feature-list">
							<li>Sleek and organized design</li>
							<li>Dedicated shoe storage</li>
							<li>Uniform hanging space</li>
							<li>Personal item compartments</li>
							<li>Professional appearance</li>
							<li>Space-efficient layout</li>
						</ul>
						<h3>Why Wood for Basketball?</h3>
						<p>The warm, professional appearance of wood lockers creates an elite atmosphere that matches the prestige of top basketball programs. The clean design helps maintain organization and team culture.</p>
						<a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Get Basketball Locker Quote</a>
					</div>
					<div class="sport-detail-image">
						<div class="image-placeholder">
							<span>Basketball Locker Installation</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

