						<ul class="feature-list">
							<li>Organized storage solutions</li>
							<li>Equipment-specific compartments</li>
							<li>Uniform and gear organization</li>
							<li>Easy access to all equipment</li>
							<li>Professional appearance</li>
							<li>Durable construction</li>
						</ul>
						<h3>Why Wood for Baseball?</h3>
						<p>Wood lockers provide the professional appearance that baseball programs expect, while the customizable design allows for team-specific organization that matches each program's needs.</p>
						<a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Get Baseball Locker Quote</a>
